      "rationale": "Flow rates controlled to ±0.05 LPM via Coriolis meter; rotational speed controlled to ±5 RPM. Fluid temperature maintained at 37±0.5°C. Bovine blood viscosity and density measured at test temperature and matched in CFD inputs. All five operating points confirmed within tolerance. All experiments conducted on nominal, unaged hardware."
